33
00:01:42,106 --> 00:01:44,346
You can search by
tag as shown here,


34
00:01:45,086 --> 00:01:47,386
you type your search tags
there and you will be displayed


35
00:01:47,386 --> 00:01:49,906
that files with those
tags will be displayed.


36
00:01:50,266 --> 00:01:54,406
