00:25:57,756 --> 00:26:00,616
That timer will now start
going off every 10 seconds,


581
00:26:01,176 --> 00:26:03,456
so you know it's really
going to be sleeping.


582
00:26:04,256 --> 00:26:06,536
Another thing that
happens is apps


